  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a bain-marie, combine 2 large sweet potatoes with 2 tbsp of olive oil and 1 tsp of minced garlic. Bake for 45 minutes or until tender.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together 1 can of chickpeas, 1 cup of brown rice, 1 cup of mixed vegetables, 2 tbsp of vegan white wine vinegar, 1 tsp of dried oregano, 1 tsp of smoked paprika, 1 tsp of salt, and 1 tsp of black pepper.",
    "In a large baking dish, arrange a layer of the sweet potato mixture, followed by a layer of the chickpea mixture, and repeat until all ingredients are used, finishing with a layer of sweet potatoes on top.",
    "Sprinkle nutritional yeast and chopped fresh parsley on top of the sweet potatoes.",
    "Bake in the oven for 30 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
